## **Step 7: Power BI Measures for Contamination Analysis**

```dax
// Total Contamination
Total Contamination = 
    [CONTAMINATION_TEST_BUT_GH] + 
    [CONTAMINATION_CONTROL_BUT_GH] + 
    [CONTAMINATION_GH_BUT_NOT_IN_CM]

// Contamination Rate
Contamination Rate = 
DIVIDE(
    [Total Contamination],
    [TOTAL_TEST_CUSTOMERS] + [TOTAL_CONTROL_CUSTOMERS] + [TOTAL_GLOBAL_HOLDOUT_CUSTOMERS],
    0
)

// Campaigns with Contamination
Campaigns with Contamination = 
CALCULATE(
    DISTINCTCOUNT('FinalTable'[CAMPAIGN_NAME]),
    'FinalTable'[TOTAL_CONTAMINATION] > 0
)

// GH Alignment Gap
GH Alignment Gap = 
[TOTAL_GLOBAL_HOLDOUT_CUSTOMERS] - [TOTAL_GH_PER_CUSTOMER_MASTER]

// GH Alignment %
GH Alignment % = 
DIVIDE(
    [TOTAL_GLOBAL_HOLDOUT_CUSTOMERS],
    [TOTAL_GH_PER_CUSTOMER_MASTER],
    0
) - 1
```

